@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_znpkii(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.04 - v1 + 0.27)) / (v0 * v0))
    v0 = wp.exp(v1)
    v1 = ((0.77 / v2) + 0.77)
    v2 = 0.98
    tmp = 0.30
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.sin(v2 + 0.69) / wp.exp(v2 + 0.63)))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.cos(tmp + 0.02) / (v0 + 0.34 - v1 + 0.77)))
    data[tid] = v0
